msgid "Product-oriented backend engineer and founder. 3+ years designing systems with scalability and cost in mind, and shipping products from idea to real users."
msgstr "Mahsulotga yo'naltirilgan backend muhandis va asoschi. 3+ yil davomida masshtablilik va xarajatni hisobga olib tizimlar loyihalayman, mahsulotlarni g'oyadan haqiqiy foydalanuvchilargacha yetkazaman."

msgid "Experience"
msgstr "Tajriba"

msgid "2025 — now · Finora"
msgstr "2025 — hozir · Finora"

msgid "Co-founder / Operations Director / Backend Developer"
msgstr "Hammuassis / Operatsiyalar direktori / Backend dasturchi"

msgid "Promoted from backend to Ops Director for driving systemic improvements."
msgstr "Tizimli yaxshilanishlar uchun backend'dan Ops Director'gacha ko'tarildim."

msgid "Redesigned architecture with Redis, Celery and rate limiting."
msgstr "Redis, Celery va rate limiting bilan arxitekturani qayta loyihaladim."

msgid "Built mapping + parsing layer serving ~80% of requests without the LLM."
msgstr "So'rovlarning ~80% ini LLM'siz bajaradigan mapping + parsing qatlamini qurdim."

msgid "Cut tokens from 15–20k to 1–2k per request and cost by ~15×."
msgstr "Token sarfini 15–20k dan 1–2k gacha va xarajatni ~15× ga kamaytirdim."

msgid "2025 — now · UstozHub"
msgstr "2025 — hozir · UstozHub"

msgid "Founder / Backend Developer"
msgstr "Asoschi / Backend dasturchi"

msgid "Built an education platform from scratch — architecture, MVP, infra solo."
msgstr "Ta'lim platformasini noldan qurdim — arxitektura, MVP, infratuzilma yakka o'zim."

msgid "100k+ visits and 200+ registered teachers."
msgstr "100k+ tashrif va 200+ ro'yxatdan o'tgan o'qituvchi."

msgid "2025 · FoodSave"
msgstr "2025 · FoodSave"

msgid "Founder / Product & Backend Lead"
msgstr "Asoschi / Mahsulot va backend yetakchisi"

msgid "Bootstrapped a startup, onboarded 60+ vendors, reached first sales."
msgstr "Startapni o'zim ishga tushirdim, 60+ sotuvchini ulagandim, birinchi sotuvlarga yetdim."

msgid "Shut it down after honest analysis of market fit and unit economics."
msgstr "Bozorga moslik va birlik iqtisodini halol tahlil qilib loyihani yopdim."

msgid "2024 · TalimOne"
msgstr "2024 · TalimOne"

msgid "Backend Developer / System Designer"
msgstr "Backend dasturchi / Tizim dizayneri"

msgid "Built and sold a commercial CRM for a learning center."
msgstr "O'quv markaz uchun tijorat CRM ishlab chiqib sotdim."

msgid "400+ active students, full role system and analytics."
msgstr "400+ faol talaba, to'liq rol tizimi va analitika."

msgid "2024 · Uzcard"
msgstr "2024 · Uzcard"

msgid "Backend Developer Intern"
msgstr "Backend dasturchi (intern)"

msgid "Automated bank request processing (100–1000/day) with forms and auto-SQL."
msgstr "Bank so'rovlarini (kuniga 100–1000) shakl va avto-SQL bilan avtomatlashtirdim."

msgid "Reduced the team needed from 10 people to 2."
msgstr "Kerakli jamoa hajmini 10 odamdan 2 ga kamaytirdim."

msgid "Future goals"
msgstr "Maqsadlar"

msgid "Launch a product that reaches a million users, stay close to the craft, and keep writing openly about the work."
msgstr "Million foydalanuvchiga yetadigan mahsulotni ishga tushirish, ish mahoratiga yaqin qolish va ish haqida ochiq yozishda davom etish."

